## Data Flow: Single Simulation Request

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  POST /api/simulate                                                │
│  { "conflict": "Iran vs Israel", "enable_search": true }           │
└──────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                       │
    ┌──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │                  │                                          │
    ▼                  ▼                                          ▼
Step 1: Baseline    Step 2: Decompose                     Step 3-5: Round 1
1 AI call           1 AI call (turbo)                     3 AI calls (max)
no KB               returns sub-questions                 each with role-filtered KB
no search           returns conflict parties              each with enable_search
                       │                                      │
                       └──────────────┬───────────────────────┘
                                      │
    ┌─────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────┐
    ▼                                 ▼                          ▼
Step 6: Detect              Step 7: Cross-Examine        Step 8: Synthesize
1 AI call (turbo)           0-3 AI calls (max)           1 AI call (max)
finds disagreements         targeted rebuttals           weighted forecast
returns list of disputes    agents revise or defend      returns final JSON
    │                                 │                          │
    └─────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────┘
                                      │
                                      ▼
                        ┌─────────────────────────┐
                        │  Result JSON (~5KB)     │
                        │  baseline, round1,      │
                        │  round2, final, metrics │
                        └─────────────────────────┘
```

